data.description: Step back in time in the classic West Marin Victorian located in the heart if the San Geronimo Valley. This beautiful Lagunitas retreat offer a total of 4 Bedrooms & 3 Baths; with three bedroom / two bath main residence + a detached one bed / one bath guest cottage / ADU. This beautiful property is set on approx. .4059 acres along the San Geronimo / Papermill Creek in a stunning garden setting. This is truly a unique property in one of the valleys best neighborhoods.      This destination property offers the perfect balance of Northern California living for both indoor and outdoor living, all just minutes from downtown Fairfax and at the gateway to some of West Marin's best parks and open space preserves - some of the best recreational areas in the Bay Area.
